title: Journey To You: A Step-by-Step Guide to Becoming Who You
description:
Journey To You: A Step-by-Step Guide to Becoming Who You Were Born to Be by Steve Olsher
2010 | ISBN: 0984479600 | English | 248 pages | PDF | 3.80 MB

Steve Olsher, Founder of The Reinvention Workshop and host of Reinvention Radio, reveals the principles and exercises he's field-tested for over 20 years in this life-changing and transformative book that guides you to become who you were born to be.

Winner of the prestigious USA Book News' "Self-Help Book of the Year Award," Journey To You has been described as "What Color Is Your Parachute? meets The Secret in 21st Century form and enables readers to realize permanent, positive change without the ineffective go out and change your life banter too often found in many self-help manifestos."
